Local Chief Executive direct the Bids and Awards Committee and its Secretariat, Accounting Office and the Engineering Office submit the lacking documents;
Management consider the timelines of project implementation and improve its monitoring functions or supervision for projects being implemented to avoid the incurrence of delays; and
Management strictly adhere to the above-cited provisions of RA No. 9184 and its IRR and the DILG Memorandum Circular in the implementation of the projects;

